channel.title: Signing Onto Server
channel.description:
well i've been editing my new server for quite a while, and i think it was either yesterday or the day before that i started getting this problem.
:: lets say i log on, then i log off really quick, or log out 10 mins later, etc. it won't let me back on? it says no response from server, now im not really concerned if (I) myself can't get on, but other players, which i haven't tested out, but i still need to be on the server itself to make changes and etc.
i get this
[code]Starting Project X Scape on 0.0.0.0:43594 ClientHandler: Accepted Connection Fully ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:2738 Client type: low memory version UserId: 4925389 teh x n00b is signing onto server. LOADED: 0 [client-1-teh x n00b]: Case 130: 0 [client-1-teh x n00b]: Case 185: 9154 Game saved for player teh x n00b ClientHandler: Client teh x n00b disconnected. ClientHandler: Rejected localhost:2739 ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:2739 [/code]
i really don't see whats wrong, no errors when i compile, when i run. i must of messed something up in player.java or client.java. so if anyone could help? i would appreciate it. =)
